Fantastic Trip - 3 days 2 nights
Jan 2020
Halong Bay is a fantastic trip. We had the boat booked for our tour group (10 people) We had a great time aboard the boat. The accommodation was of a very high standard. The chef was amazing and the food was excellent. We had a workshop showing us how to make fish net decoration from carrots and the flowers from carrot and cucumber. The staff were friendly and couldn't do enough for you. If you have a chance to take one of the cruises it is worth it. We were also taken to the boats that take you through the caves, which are stunning. The only downside is the number of properties being built along the quayside. I hope they don't spoil this lovely area.
